---
// Section 4 — Personal / "Who is Sosaiah?" (Figma frame 72:81, PAGE 04)
---

<section id="personal" class="frame frame--alt">
  <div class="canvas">
    <!-- Portrait -->
    <img class="abs portrait" src="/images/kid2.JPG" alt="Sosaiah"
      style="left:0;top:27.5px;width:478px;height:845px" />

    <!-- Title -->
    <div class="title">
      <h2 class="heading abs" data-parallax="left" style="left:692px;top:98px">WHO</h2>
      <h2 class="heading abs" data-parallax="right" style="left:868px;top:98px">IS</h2>
      <h2 class="heading abs" style="left:854px;top:151px">SOSAIAH?</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Goals -->
    <div class="group">
      <h2 class="heading abs" style="left:591px;top:292px">GOALS</h2>
      <p class="abs body serif" style="left:537px;top:345px;width:262px">
        I hope to enter the tech industry and contribute to the actualisation of fun and interesting
        products.<br /><br />My greater goal is to have my own non-profit organisation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Hobbies -->
    <div class="group">
      <h2 class="heading abs" style="left:1170px;top:501px">HOBBIES</h2>
      <p class="abs body serif" style="left:1116px;top:554px;width:262px">
        I love to enjoy life. I love to play sports (bouldering, soccer, basketball, boxing), read
        philosophy, and play games with my friends (Fortnite enjoyer).
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Design note -->
    <p class="abs body serif" style="left:690px;top:695px;width:262px">
      I would love to be able to design unique and artistic websites. Though I am not
      <span class="serif-bold">yet</span> very good at it.
    </p>

    <!-- Snapshot + see more -->
    <div class="aside">
      <img class="abs snapshot" src="/images/water.JPG" alt=""
        style="left:843px;top:372px;width:233px;height:155px" />
      <p class="abs see-more" style="left:1125px;top:636px;width:243px">
        <span class="type-bold see-more-top">want to see more?</span><br />
        <span class="see-more-sub">(don’t click, website under construction)</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="page-num" style="left:1352px;top:842px">PAGE 04</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .heading { width: auto; white-space: nowrap; }
  .portrait,
  .snapshot { object-fit: cover; opacity: 0.8; }
  .body { font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; color: var(--ink); }
  .see-more { text-align: center; color: var(--ink); }
  .see-more-top { font-size: 16px; }
  .see-more-sub { font-family: var(--font-type); font-weight: 400; font-size: 12px; }

  .title,
  .group,
  .aside { display: contents; }

  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .title {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0 14px;
    }
    .group {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .aside {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .portrait { aspect-ratio: 478 / 845; max-width: 300px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .snapshot { aspect-ratio: 233 / 155; max-width: 260px; }
    .body { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.55; }
    .see-more { width: auto !important; }
  }
</style>
